# Raw timestamped captures from ForegroundPostTeleportWindowRecorder /
# BackgroundPostTeleportWindowRecorder. Each test run that sets
# WWOW_CAPTURE_POST_TELEPORT_WINDOW=1 or WWOW_CAPTURE_BG_POST_TELEPORT_WINDOW=1
# emits one of these per teleport observed; only the curated *_baseline.json
# files belong in source control.
foreground_20*.json
background_20*.json
